My neighbor is a Sheep 🐑 Herder as well as the gentleman who sold me my little piece of land down here,,
one day He was out with his sheep and we got to talking about a snake issue we were having at the time and he told me a story about a snake called #alicante that drinks the milk from the breast of mammals,, he told me a story about his Mother being pregnant with him and the snake 🐍 coming and whistling at her while she was washing clothes in the river ,, the snakes getting into the pins with mama cows ,, 
truly truly strange stories and I was sure it was not true… 

The Alicante is a “fictional” Mexican snake that drinks mother’s milk and impregnates women, or uses the human stomach as a living place.

“Unlike most snakes, Alicantes supposedly don’t drag and crawl upon their entire bodies, but move in a tall and erect fashion, with the majority of their body upright.”
“When women are recovering from the miracle of childbirth, the Alicante has been known to sneak into the new mother’s bedroom under cover of darkness, often while she is in a state of lactation and nursing her newborn child. The viper first hypnotizes the newborn with its rattle tail, eventually pacifying the child and placing the rattle in the kid’s mouth, keeping it entertained and quiet, as the asp sucks the milk out of the nursing mother’s breast. And after falling in love with a woman, it is purported to insert its rattle into a woman’s sleeping mouth, while inserting it’s own mouth into the woman’s nether region.”
This snake also has a loud whistle, sucks milk from the cows, and can travel through long grass using only half its body, with its head above the grass like a submarine conning tower. All round, quite an extraordinary creature I would say!

Anyway - this is my version of an Alicante.

Awhile back 

A sign is a token of meaning that stands for a known entity,, by this definition Language is a system of signs,Not Symbols 
  A Symbol on the other hand is an image or representation which points toward something essentially Unknown, a Mystery. 
A sign communicates Abstract/Objective meaning whereas a Symbol conveys Living, breathing, subjective meaning…  EddyEdDingrrr

And with that I mind i must admit this looks nothing like the transcendental object-energy it symbolizes 😜🕉️🎶🖼️🪨🔔🌊🪞

Thanks Fip! This is the 1st one I made at my last trip to the Mighty @lifetimetattoosd 

..cool story that lead to Fip getting #billiken Tattooed— in 2017 I was walking down 14th Avenue In Denver Colorado to get my afternoon coffee and spotted a sign 🪧 saying there was an estate sale around the corner ,, I obliged and payed heed to sign ,  waltzed in and immediately I was greeted by the most beautiful and Magical Purple conical Hat I had never seen.. I gathered the Hat of the dead wizard and some dolls from different places across the Globe that the #meinengers had collected ,  I also found a couple FezS, some glassware and table shaped like a painter’s palette 🎨,, tangent alert- the Magical Purple Hat bore the initials “ROJ” Denver 138 and had a golden pin with the image of #billiken (I had seen him before but couldn’t place him), I didn’t know at the time these are the initials for a fraternal organization that Fip’s Dad was a member of,,, long story short er,, that Hat finding me that day lead me to spreading immeasurable amounts of MIRTH to random folks,strangers and friends alike ,, and led me to a love for Billiken as an ambassador of said Mirthful vibes,,, that and the conical vortex made of purple felt were what led up to me Tattooing @fipbuchanan a true San Diego OG in every sense of the word.. I have always and will always have respect and love for that AND those that came before me in The Craft,, Now this might not mean that much to you but for me it was just pure fucking Tattoo Magic,, listening to Him and Rob aka @lifetimetattoo tell stories is just about as cool as it gets for me,, 
  God gave me 2 ears and 1 mouth for a reason and even though I’ve been doing this for over 30 years now I never miss the chance to learn something or just laugh my ass off about #enthusiastic acts of love 😂 etc etc #insidejoke 

This is the tale of the hat of a dead wizard and how it’s morphogenetic energy created and produced Happiness out of thin air ,, and what a cool way to celebrate the life of your Dad - thanks for letting me Share that with ya Fip,, next time I’m coming to @avalontattoo_2 to get Yatted up from You!
